1. *Upalilo* mi se svetlo. (The light *turned on* for me.)
2. Kada *upalimo* televizor, uvek gledamo vesti. (When we *turn on* the TV, we always watch the news.)
3. Juče sam slučajno *upalila* mikrotalasnu umesto rerne. (Yesterday I accidentally *turned on* the microwave instead of the oven.)
4. Nisam siguran da li sam dobro *upalio* ovaj program. (I'm not sure if I *turned on* the right program.)
5. *Upalila* sam alarm da me probudi ujutru. (I *set* the alarm to wake me up in the morning.)
6. Ako ti je hladno, *upalim* grejanje. (If you're cold, I'll *turn on* the heating.)
7. Da li si *upalio* alarm u kući kada si odlazio? (Did you *activate* the alarm in the house when you were leaving?)
8. Molim te, *upalite* računare pre nego što sednete za stol. (Please *turn on* the computers before you sit down.)
9. Naš auto neće *upaliti* kada je hladno. (Our car won't *start* when it's cold.)
10. Kad se *upalio* požar, svi su počeli da beže. (When the fire *started*, everyone began to run away.)